(b) X(a, b, c) ≡ a.b.c + a.b.c + c,

(c) P(a, b, c, d) ≡ ((d + a) + (d.a)) → d + a + c.d(a + d).d.c
(d) M(a, b, c, d) ≡ (a + b + c).a → (c.d).d
